Michael Goodman is a gynecologist who sees patients at his office, ["Caring for Women"] in ["Oak Tree Plaza"], where the ["Covell" Covell Blvd.] ["Nugget" Nugget Market] is located.  

Dr. Goodman specializes in perimenopausal and menopausal medicine, hormone replacement and alternatives, and sexual problems (in this area he also sees men for consultation).  He also performs in-office bone density exams and vaginal ultrasounds.

Dr. Goodman is also one of Davis' ["Published Authors"] with his book, "The Midlife Bible:  A Woman's Survival Guide."

See his [http://caringforwomyn.com/ web site] for further information.
